DIE veteraan- radio- en TV-aanbieder Mark Pilgrim het sy stryd met kanker verloor. Lloyd Madurai, besturende direkteur van HOT 102.7FM, het in 'n verklaring die nuus bevestig. "Ons held en broer en geliefde radiopersoonlikheid Mark Pilgrim het sy stryd met kanker vanoggend om 10:45 verloor," het Madurai gesÃª. "Hy het dapper tot die einde baklei. Mark het vreedsaam by die huis gesterf by sy verloofde Adrienne. Hulle was saam vir sy laaste asem." Pilgrim (53) is in Maart 2022 met fase 4 longkanker gediagnoseer. - News24 My heart is shattered. Mark Pilgrim has just passed away. My friend, you fought so hard. ?? RIP Mark PilgrimYou, Sir, *lived through illness* till the end.A great creative and audio legend.Condolences to friends, family and colleagues. ?? pic.twitter.com/MTUsMIAhNj Rest In Peace, Mark Pilgrim. Your memory lives on forever ?? pic.twitter.com/p6YpHPrfVs Beloved radio presenter Mark Pilgrim has sadly passed away.Pilgrim, who was battling stage four cancer at the time of his passing, will always be remembered for touching the lives of millions of people, both on and off the air.Rest in Peace, Mark Pilgrim. pic.twitter.com/1kyEgI6XJu Beloved radio presenter Mark Pilgrim has sadly passed away.Pilgrim, who was battling stage four cancer at the time of his passing, will always be remembered for touching the lives of millions of people, both on and off the air.Rest in Peace, Mark Pilgrim. pic.twitter.com/v18kYlXGEI 